</TABLE><P></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rtfm>rtfm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/5/01 7:39:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dueling Tactics. Druid vs Wizard?</span><hr size=1> If he has any MR at all, you are going to have a hard time sticking your snare.<br>
